the ghost and mrs. muir is a 1947 american comedy film directed by joseph l. mankiewicz . the film is a remake of the 1947 film the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) . the film is based on the novel the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) , the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) , the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) , the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) , the ghost & mrs. muir ( 1947 ) .